{
  "title": "Warmly Spiced Uruguayan Pak Choi Stew",
  "description": "A malty and chewy Uruguayan dish featuring pak choi, this stew is perfect for adventurous eaters, this slow cook recipe is egg free friendly and full of flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
